descriptionHtml:
Heya, this is the new Foresters Axe, modeled in Blender, textures photographed and
edited in Photoshop CS6 by me!

READ THIS:
The axe isent actually placed in the map, you have to craft it, or to cget it via console!
Heres the console command:  

player.additem 13000D63 1

Changes for 1.1:
-fixed that the axe was invisible in-game (thanks to ForestTech for reporting ans solving this bug)

Yesterday I remembered that this model was still on my external harddrive, used two years
ago as a movie asset, for a private film project.. So, finally, I thought, this must be in Skyrim,
and here it is!

I hope you will have some fun with it, if you find any bugs, report them to me, i will
see if I can fix them!
Critic is very very welcome, please tell me what you think about the Foresters Axe:)
author: David Jungnickel
